MERRICK FOR MICHAEL 7
---------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/a456180e495c68c8628e1ed739b9da62.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/34225

When you need a hard edge to see you through the lost days...there's no one that can navigate the roads and pitfalls better. No one willing to take the risks and come out on the other side. A bit crazy, a bit battered---and he's still standing... Terrifyingly loyal, there's no place he'd rather be than right on the cutting edge. And there's no one he'd rather be with than MynX, fighting his way across the broken land... Is he a man or one of the four horsemen...?  You decide
